channel.title: How do i change the starters on my server?
channel.description: Im new to coding as you all could probably tell and im starting on a blank client. How would i change that so we start other objects.

item.title: How do i change the starters on my server?
item.dc:creator: @Mendorphins Mendorphins
item.description:
@Mendorphins wrote:

No, I see where you’re getting confused… a server comes with a file called “client.java” I think this is just where the server communicates with the client. You’ll have a client.java in your client folder too.

You can distinguish the two by looking for server.java, if it has that it’s your server folder. If it just has class 1, class 2, class 3 etc. etc., it’s your client folder.
